{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3312250/extras/title-01.png?t=1739739644\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Dive into an alternate <i>World War II era setting</i>, where <strong>dieselpunk</strong> technology and eldritch horrors collide.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Powered by Unreal Engine 5</strong> and latest technologies.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3312250/extras/room_framed_opt.gif?t=1739739644\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3312250/extras/title-02.png?t=1739739644\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">When you see monsters, corpses, or are covered in darkness - your <strong>FEAR</strong> increases, and if you do not take care of it - soon you will become a <strong>GHOUL</strong>.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Reduce your <strong>FEAR</strong> with alcohol, keep generator lights on, and take care of your teammates with a good punch of the holy book.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3312250/extras/beer_and_ghoul_framed_opt__beer_cutted_.gif?t=1739739644\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3312250/extras/title-03.png?t=1739739644\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Like in <i>Amnesia </i>games, you can smoothly interact with doors / chests / traps. But if you have no time - <strong>DON'T HESITATE</strong> - kick it to open faster, but making more noise.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Besides taking items into your inventory, you can grab them and throw anywhere to see what happens. <i>Also your teammates can catch them in fly.</i></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">And what about an oil barrel and a flare? \ud83e\udd14</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3312250/extras/bottle_drop_framed_opt.gif?t=1739739644\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3312250/extras/title-04.png?t=1739739644\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong><i>Someone </i></strong>from your crew must become a<strong> LIGHT KEEPER</strong> and stay on the surface to refuel the bunker generator and keep an eye on the radar to notify you about any threats or valuable loot nearby.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">But be careful - <strong><i>THE GUARDIAN ENTITY DOES NOT LIKE GENERATORS</i></strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3312250/extras/corridor_lights_off_on_framed_opt.gif?t=1739739644\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3312250/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1739739644","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3312250/page.bg.jpg?t=1739739644","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3312250/27520ebe3e1edcfc695b3b5a98759c7be4f9926d/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1739739644","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3312250/27520ebe3e1edcfc695b3b5a98759c7be4f9926d/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1739739644","categori